<subSubSection id="C326E0F8A64D221638EB3C4C09002E7D" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="92" pageId="8" pageNumber="91" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8B83B373A64D221738EB3C4C0A982862" blockId="8.[189,1401,1852,2025]" box="[189,416,1852,1879]" pageId="8" pageNumber="91">
<emphasis id="B9486F61A64D221738EB3C4C0A0E2863" bold="true" box="[189,310,1852,1878]" pageId="8" pageNumber="91">Diagnosis</emphasis>
(female)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B83B373A64D221638EB3C1909002E7D" blockId="8.[189,1401,1852,2025]" lastBlockId="9.[189,1398,265,328]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="92" pageId="8" pageNumber="91">
Body length 3.0– 
<quantity id="4CC41E96A64D221739DA3C190AD228B1" box="[396,490,1897,1924]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="3.8">3.8 mm</quantity>
; antenna as long as or slightly longer than body, F15 length 2.0 × its width; anteromesoscutum rugose to rugulose; mesoscutellar disc coriaceous (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A64D22173C5C3CFB0F512890" box="[1034,1129,1931,1957]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[189,232,1963,1989]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,797,1924]" captionTargetId="figure-122@9.[189,1398,797,1924]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 3. Microplitis cebes Nixon, 1970, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0007. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Wings. E. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690336" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690336/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="91">Fig. 3C</figureCitation>
); vein R1 shorter than pterostigma (i.e., vein R1 longer than pterostigma half), 1 
<superScript id="7C491E3BA64D22173B3A3CDC084F288F" attach="left" box="[876,887,1964,1978]" fontSize="6" pageId="8" pageNumber="91">st</superScript>
discal cell length 1.0–1.2 × its width, vein 1CUb 2.3–2.5 × as long as vein 1CUa (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A64D22173AD33CBE09DB28DD" box="[645,739,1998,2024]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[189,232,1963,1989]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,797,1924]" captionTargetId="figure-122@9.[189,1398,797,1924]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 3. Microplitis cebes Nixon, 1970, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0007. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Wings. E. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690336" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690336/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="91">Fig. 3D</figureCitation>
); T1 length 2.0 × its maximum width, T1 sub-parallel- to parallel-sided (
<figureCitation id="1307AFF6A64C221639393A790AF42E16" box="[367,460,265,291]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="9.[189,232,1963,1989]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,797,1924]" captionTargetId="figure-122@9.[189,1398,797,1924]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Fig. 3. Microplitis cebes Nixon, 1970, ♀, TMUC-HBMMP0007. A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Head, dorsal view. C. Mesosoma, dorsal view. D. Wings. E. Metasoma, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690336" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690336/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="92">Fig. 3E</figureCitation>
). Colour: body black; pterostigma dark brown; legs except for metafemur and basal half of mesofemur yellow.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
